3. **Rate Limiting Per Origin**:
```php
// Layer 3: Rate limit by origin to prevent abuse
class CorsRateLimiter {
    private Redis $redis;

    public function checkLimit(string $origin): bool {
        $key = "cors_ratelimit:" . hash('sha256', $origin);
        $current = $this->redis->incr($key);

        if ($current === 1) {
            $this->redis->expire($key, 60); // 1 minute window
        }

        return $current <= 1000; // 1000 requests per minute per origin
    }
}
