Supporting subdomains requires careful validation to prevent subdomain takeover attacks. The 2023 subdomain takeover vulnerabilities in major cloud providers showed how attackers can register abandoned subdomains to bypass CORS restrictions.

**PRODUCTION PATTERN**:

